review:
Update (2022-04): The dev has removed the broken achievement, is now completable :)

[strike]Unfortunately has a broken achievement (Exotic Snacks). There's a fix in the discussions, but the dev hasn't responded since 2019.

If they see this: the problem is in GameManager.CheckOuterSpaceAchievement(), it never awards the achievement when you reach the goals. Adding something like this to the end will fix it:
	if (this.BonusInt3 >= 3 && this.BonusInt2 >= 2 && this.BonusInt1 >= 1)
	{
		StatsAndAchievementsManager.UnlockAchievement("AC_LEV7");
	}
[/strike]
